- Stop!

14:36.985 --> 14:38.844
Stop fighting. You're too old

14:38.854 --> 14:40.312
for your faces to heal properly.

14:40.322 --> 14:43.181
Now knock it off!

14:43.191 --> 14:44.950
Matthew, I'm sorry.

14:44.960 --> 14:47.018
But I need to take this managing job.

