20:00.205 --> 20:02.464
- I don't have time for this.
- Yeah, hey, can you just

20:02.474 --> 20:04.132
give us a second? I'll donate blood.

20:04.142 --> 20:06.468
So, Michael.

20:06.478 --> 20:09.137
Notice you've been posting some
inspirational quotes on Insta.

20:09.147 --> 20:11.406
- Things okay with Gregg?
- I can't believe

20:11.416 --> 20:13.008
